description: This skill enables you to say what type of mama joke you want back. The joke categories include: fat, dumb, old, and ugly. More categories will be added weekly. This skill may not be suitable for all ages.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask yo mama how old is her mama
Alexa, ask yo mama to tell me a joke
Alexa, ask yo mama to say a joke
name: Yo Mama
shortDescription: This skill enables you to say what type of mama joke you want back.
